  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "劉旻，漢高祖母弟也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "初名崇，為人美須髯，目重瞳子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "少無賴，嗜酒好博，嘗黥為卒。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "高祖事晉為河東節度使，以旻為都指揮使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "高祖即帝位，以為太原尹、北京留守、同中書門下平章事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "隱帝時，累加中書令。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "隱帝少，政在大臣，周太祖為樞密使，新討三叛，立大功，而與旻素有隙，旻頗不自安，謂判官鄭珙曰：「主上幼弱，政在權臣，而吾與郭公不葉，時事如何？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "」珙曰：「漢政將亂矣！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "晉陽兵雄天下，而地形險固，十州征賦足以自給。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "公為宗室，不以此時為計，後必為人所制。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "」旻曰：「子言，乃吾意也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "」乃罷上供征賦，收豪傑，籍丁民以益兵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "三年，周太祖起魏，隱帝遇弒，旻乃謀舉兵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "周太祖之自魏入也，反狀已白，而漢大臣不即推尊之，故未敢即立，乃白漢太后，立旻子赟為漢嗣，遣宰相馮道迎赟於徐州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "當是時，人皆知太祖之非實意也，旻獨喜曰：「吾兒為帝矣，何患！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "」乃罷兵，遣人至京師。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "周太祖少賤，黥其頸上為飛雀，世謂之郭雀兒。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "太祖見旻使者，具道所以立赟之意，因自指其頸以示使者曰：「自古豈有雕青天子？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "幸公無以我為疑。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "」旻喜，益信以為然。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "太原少尹李驤曰：「郭公舉兵犯順，其勢不能為漢臣，必不為劉氏立後。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "」因勸旻以兵下太行，控孟津以俟變，庶幾赟得立，赟立而罷兵可也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "旻大罵曰：「驤腐儒，欲離間我父子！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "」命左右牽出斬之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "驤臨刑嘆曰：「吾為愚人畫計，死誠宜矣！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "然吾妻病，不可獨存，願與之俱死。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "」旻聞之，即並戮其妻於市，以其事白漢，以明無他。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "已而周太祖果代漢，降封赟湘陰公。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "旻遣牙將李鋋奉書周太祖，求赟歸太原，而赟已死。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "旻慟哭，為李驤立祠，歲時祠之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "已而兀欲為述軋所弒，述律代立。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "旻遣樞密直學士王得中聘於述律，求兵以攻周。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "述律遣蕭禹厥率兵五萬助旻。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "旻出陰地攻晉州，為王峻所敗。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "是歲大寒，旻軍凍餒，亡失過半。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "明年，又攻府州，為折德扆所敗，德扆因取岢嵐軍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "周太祖崩，旻聞之喜，遣使乞兵於契丹。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "契丹遣楊袞將鐵馬萬騎及奚諸部兵五六萬人號稱十萬以助旻。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "旻以張元徽為先鋒，自將騎兵三萬攻潞州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0040",
          "zh": "潞州李筠遣穆令鈞以步騎三千拒元徽於太平驛，元徽擊敗之，益圍潞州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0041",
          "zh": "是時，世宗新即位，以謂旻幸周有大喪，而天子新立，必不能出兵，宜自將以擊其不意。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0042",
          "zh": "自宰相馮道等多言不可，世宗意甚銳。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0043",
          "zh": "顯德元年三月親征，甲午，戰於高平，李重進、白重贊將左，樊愛能、何徽將右，向訓、史彥超居中軍，張永德以禁兵衛蹕。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0044",
          "zh": "旻亦列為三陣，張元徽居東偏，楊袞居西偏，旻居其中。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0045",
          "zh": "袞望周師謂旻曰：「敵也，未可輕動。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0046",
          "zh": "」旻奮髯曰：「時不可失，無妄言也！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0047",
          "zh": "」袞怒而去。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0048",
          "zh": "旻號令東偏先進，王得中叩馬諫曰：「南風甚急，非北軍之利也，宜少待之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0049",
          "zh": "」旻怒曰：「老措大，毋妄沮吾軍！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0050",
          "zh": "」即麾元徽，元徽擊周右軍，兵始交，愛能、徽退走，其騎軍亂，步卒數千棄甲叛降元徽，呼萬歲聲振川谷。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0051",
          "zh": "世宗大駭，躬督戰士，士皆奮命爭先，而風勢愈盛，旻自麾赤幟收軍，軍不可遏，旻遂敗。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0052",
          "zh": "日暮，旻收余兵萬人阻澗而止。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0053",
          "zh": "是時，周之後軍，劉詞將之，在後未至，而世宗銳於速戰，戰已勝，詞軍繼至，因乘勝追擊之，旻又大敗，輜重器甲、乘輿服御物皆為周師所獲。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0054",
          "zh": "旻獨乘契丹黃騮，自雕窠嶺間道馳去，夜失道山谷間，得村民為鄉導，誤趨平陽，得他道以歸，而張元徽戰歿於陣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0055",
          "zh": "楊袞怒旻，按兵西偏不戰，故獨全軍而返。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0056",
          "zh": "旻歸，為黃騮治廄，飾以金銀，食以三品料，號「自在將軍」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0057",
          "zh": "世宗休軍潞州，大宴將士，斬敗將樊愛能、何徽等七十餘人，軍威大振。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0058",
          "zh": "進攻太原，遣符彥卿、史彥超北控忻口，以斷契丹援路。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0059",
          "zh": "太原城方四十里，周師去城三百步，圍之匝，自四月至於六月，攻之不克，而彥卿等為契丹所敗，彥超戰歿，世宗遽班師。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0060",
          "zh": "初，周師圍城也，旻遣王得中送楊袞以歸，因乞援兵於契丹，契丹發數萬騎助旻，遣得中先還。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0061",
          "zh": "至代州，代州將桑珪殺防禦使鄭處謙，以城降周，並送得中於周。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0062",
          "zh": "世宗召問得中虜助兵多少，得中言送袞歸，無所求也，世宗信之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0063",
          "zh": "已而契丹敗符彥卿於忻口，得中遂見殺。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0064",
          "zh": "旻自敗於高平，已而被圍，以憂得疾，明年十一月卒，年六十，子承鈞立。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0065",
          "zh": "承鈞，旻次子也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0066",
          "zh": "少頗好學，工書。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0067",
          "zh": "旻卒，承鈞遣人奉表契丹，自稱男。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0068",
          "zh": "述律答之以詔，呼承鈞為兒，許其嗣位。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0069",
          "zh": "初，旻常謂張元徽等曰：「吾以高祖之業，赟之冤，義不為郭公屈爾，期與公等勉力以復家國之仇。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0070",
          "zh": "至於稱帝一方，豈獲已也，顧我是何天子，爾亦是何節度使？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0071",
          "zh": "」故其僭號仍稱乾祐，不改元，不立宗廟，四時之祭，用家人禮。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0072",
          "zh": "承鈞既立，始赦境內，改乾祐十年曰天會元年，立七廟於顯聖宮。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0073",
          "zh": "契丹遣高勛助承鈞，承鈞遣李存瑰與勛攻上黨，無所得而還。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0074",
          "zh": "明年，世宗北伐契丹，下三關，契丹使來告急，承鈞將發兵，而世宗班師，乃已。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0075",
          "zh": "宋興，昭義節度使李筠叛命，遣其將劉繼沖、判官孫孚奉表稱臣，執其監軍周光遜、李廷玉送於太原，乞兵為援。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0076",
          "zh": "承鈞欲謀於契丹，繼沖道筠意，請無用契丹兵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0077",
          "zh": "承鈞即率其國兵自將出團柏谷，群臣餞之汾水。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0078",
          "zh": "僕射趙華曰：「李筠舉事輕易，陛下不圖成敗，空國興師，臣實憂之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0079",
          "zh": "」承鈞至太平驛，封筠隴西郡王。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0080",
          "zh": "筠見承鈞儀衛不備，非如王者，悔臣之，筠因自陳受周氏恩，不忍背德。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0081",
          "zh": "而承鈞與周世仇也，聞筠言亦不悅。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0082",
          "zh": "遣宣徽使盧贊監其軍，筠心益不平，與贊多不葉，承鈞遣宰相衛融和解之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0083",
          "zh": "已而筠敗死，衛融被執至京師，太祖皇帝問融承鈞所以助筠反狀，融言不遜，太祖命以鐵楇擊其首，流血被面，融呼曰：「臣得死所矣！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0084",
          "zh": "」太祖顧左右曰：「此忠臣也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0085",
          "zh": "」釋之，命以良藥傅其瘡。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0086",
          "zh": "遣融致書於承鈞，求周光遜等，約亦歸融太原。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0087",
          "zh": "承鈞不報，融遂留京師。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0088",
          "zh": "承鈞謂趙華曰：「不聽公言，幾至於敗。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0089",
          "zh": "然失衛融、盧贊，吾以為恨爾。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0090",
          "zh": "承鈞由此益重儒者，以抱腹山人郭無為參議國政。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0091",
          "zh": "無為，棣州人，方顙鳥喙，好學多聞，善談辯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0092",
          "zh": "嘗衣褐為道士，居武當山。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0093",
          "zh": "周太祖討李守貞於河中，無為詣軍門上謁，詢以當世之務，太祖奇之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0094",
          "zh": "或謂太祖曰：「公為漢大臣，握重兵居外，而延縱橫之士，非所以防微慮遠之道也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0095",
          "zh": "」由是太祖不納。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0096",
          "zh": "無為去，隱抱腹山。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0097",
          "zh": "承鈞內樞密使段常識之，薦其材，承鈞以諫議大夫召之，遂以為相。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0098",
          "zh": "五年，宿衛殿直行首王隱、劉紹、趙鸞等謀作亂，事覺被誅，其詞連段常，乃罷常樞密為汾州刺史，縊殺之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0099",
          "zh": "自旻世凡舉事必稟契丹，而承鈞之立多略。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0100",
          "zh": "契丹遣使者責承鈞改元、援李筠、殺段常不以告，承鈞惶恐謝罪。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0101",
          "zh": "使者至契丹輒見留，承鈞奉之愈謹，而契丹待承鈞益薄。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0102",
          "zh": "承鈞自李筠敗而失契丹之援，無復南侵之意。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0103",
          "zh": "地狹產薄，以歲輸契丹，故國用日削，乃拜五臺山僧繼颙為鴻臚卿。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0104",
          "zh": "繼颙，故燕王劉守光之子，守光之死，以孽子得不殺，削髮為浮圖，後居五臺山，為人多智，善商財利，自旻世頗以賴之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0105",
          "zh": "繼颙能講《華嚴經》，四方供施，多積畜以佐國用。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0106",
          "zh": "五臺當契丹界上，繼颙常得其馬以獻，號「添都馬」，歲率數百匹。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0107",
          "zh": "又於柏谷置銀冶，募民鑿山取礦，烹銀以輸，劉氏仰以足用，即其冶建寶興軍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0108",
          "zh": "繼颙後累官至太師、中書令，以老病卒，追封定王。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0109",
          "zh": "太祖皇帝嘗因界上諜者謂承鈞曰：「君家與周氏為世仇，宜其不屈，今我與爾無所間，何為困此一方之人也？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0110",
          "zh": "若有志於中國，宜下太行以決勝負。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0111",
          "zh": "」承鈞遣諜者復命曰：「河東土地兵甲，不足以當中國之十一；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0112",
          "zh": "然承鈞家世非叛者，區區守此，蓋懼漢氏之不血食也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0113",
          "zh": "」太祖哀其言，笑謂諜者曰：「為我語承鈞，開爾一路以為生。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0114",
          "zh": "」故終其世不加兵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0115",
          "zh": "承鈞立十三年病卒，其養子繼恩立。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0116",
          "zh": "繼恩本姓薛氏，父釗為卒，旻以女妻之，生繼恩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0117",
          "zh": "漢高祖以釗婿也，除其軍籍，置之門下。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0118",
          "zh": "釗無材能，高祖衣食之而無所用。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0119",
          "zh": "妻以旻女常居中，釗罕得見，釗常怏怏，因醉拔佩刀刺之，傷而不死，釗即自裁。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0120",
          "zh": "旻女後適何氏，生子繼元，而何氏及旻女皆卒。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0121",
          "zh": "旻以其子承鈞無子，乃以二子命承鈞養為子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0122",
          "zh": "承鈞立，以繼恩為太原尹。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0123",
          "zh": "承鈞嘗謂郭無為曰：「繼恩純孝，然非濟世之才，恐不能了我家事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0124",
          "zh": "」無為不對。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0125",
          "zh": "承鈞病臥勤政閣，召無為，執手以後事付之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0126",
          "zh": "承鈞卒，繼恩告哀於契丹而後立。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0127",
          "zh": "繼恩服缞裳視事，寢處皆居勤政閣，而承鈞故執事百司宿衛者皆在太原府廨。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0128",
          "zh": "九月，繼恩置酒會諸大臣宗子，飲罷，臥閣中。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0129",
          "zh": "供奉官侯霸榮率十餘人挺刃入閣，閉戶而殺之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0130",
          "zh": "郭無為遣人以梯登屋入，殺霸榮並其黨。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0131",
          "zh": "初，承鈞之語郭無為也，繼恩怨無為不助己，及立，欲逐之而未果，故霸榮之亂，人皆以謂無為之謀，霸榮死，口滅而無知者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0132",
          "zh": "無為迎繼元而立之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0133",
          "zh": "繼元為人忍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0134",
          "zh": "旻子十餘人，皆無可稱者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0135",
          "zh": "當繼元時，有鎬、鍇、锜、錫、銑，於繼元為諸父，皆為繼元所殺，獨銑以佯愚獲免。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0136",
          "zh": "承鈞妻郭氏，繼元兄弟自少母之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0137",
          "zh": "繼元妻段氏，嘗以小過為郭氏所責，既而以它疾而卒，繼元疑其殺之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0138",
          "zh": "及立，遣嬖者範超圖殺郭氏，郭氏方缞服哭承鈞於柩前，超執而縊殺之，於是劉氏之子孫無遺類矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0139",
          "zh": "繼元立，改元曰廣運。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0140",
          "zh": "王師北征，繼元閉城拒守，太祖皇帝以詔書招繼元出降，許以平盧軍節度使，郭無為安國軍節度使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0141",
          "zh": "無為捧詔色動，而並人及繼元左右皆欲堅守以拒命。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0142",
          "zh": "無為仰天慟哭，拔佩刀欲自裁，為左右所持。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0143",
          "zh": "繼元自下執其手，延之上坐，無為曰：「奈何以孤城拒百萬之王師？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0144",
          "zh": "」蓋欲搖動並人，而並人守意益堅。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0145",
          "zh": "宦者衛德貴察無為有異志，以告繼元，繼元遣人縊殺之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0146",
          "zh": "初，太祖皇帝命引汾水浸其城，水自城門入，而有積草自城中飄出塞之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0147",
          "zh": "是時，王師頓兵甘草地中，會歲暑雨，軍士多疾，乃班師。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0148",
          "zh": "王師已去，繼元決城下水註之臺駘澤，水已落而城多摧圮。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0149",
          "zh": "契丹使者韓知璠時在太原，嘆曰：「王師之引水浸城也，知其一而不知其二，若先浸而後涸，則並人無類矣！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0150",
          "zh": "太平興國四年，王師復北征，繼元窮窘，而並人猶欲堅守。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0151",
          "zh": "其樞密副使馬峰老疾居於家，舁入見繼元，流涕以興亡諭之，繼元乃降。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0152",
          "zh": "太宗皇帝御城北高臺受降，以繼元為右衛上將軍，封彭城公。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0153",
          "zh": "其後事具國史。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0154",
          "zh": "〈",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0155",
          "zh": "（旻年世興滅，諸書皆同，自周廣順元年建號，至皇朝太平興國四年滅，凡二十八年，余具年譜註。）〉",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}